snippet.title: Invictus (SMW Kaizo Hack) Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch live on Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/juzcook

Here it is... The official trailer for my Super Mario World romhack, INVICTUS, releasing before the end of September. Check back here for a download link, or stay tuned in Discord/on Twitter.

INVICTUS is a chocolate kaizo hack, featuring many custom elements that will challenge even the most experienced players. This took 9 months to build from beginning to end, and features 20 levels with a few suprises.

Full soundtrack: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XFLr0mQMhhY

Join the community: https://discord.gg/ekYnHyN
Follow on Twitter: https://twitter.com/juzcook
